    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonle is a casual puzzle solving game designed to help people learn about skeletal anatomy and solve fun puzzles doing it! You can choose from a Human skeleton, a T. Rex skeleton, or a Cat skeleton to start the game, and your goal is to guess the target bone that's been selected at random.  When you make a guess, the bone will change color to show how close you are to the right answer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098630/extras/d056170d07b4da876b825b3eba01dc77.poster.avif?t=1751339460\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098630/extras/d056170d07b4da876b825b3eba01dc77.webm?t=1751339460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098630/extras/d056170d07b4da876b825b3eba01dc77.mp4?t=1751339460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Prior Knowledge Needed!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shown below is an example of the bone index, a library that tells you the <strong>simplified</strong> name for the bone and what you should type. As the difficulty increases, the bones become less and less simplified! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098630/extras/06f20af7b0dadd60fc46050ac3df877b.poster.avif?t=1751339460\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098630/extras/06f20af7b0dadd60fc46050ac3df877b.webm?t=1751339460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098630/extras/06f20af7b0dadd60fc46050ac3df877b.mp4?t=1751339460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through game unlocking new skeletons, getting trophies, comparing leaderboard scores with your friends, competing with the people at home, or buying new cosmetics with in-game currency.</p>",
